  "prompt": "What is the funniest Hindi commentary line, in cricket, you have heard recently?",
  "response": "One of the funniest Hindi commentary lines that has gained popularity in recent times is from renowned commentator Navjot Singh Sidhu. He often combines humor with insightful observations. For example, during a match, he quipped, \u201cBade bade deshon mein aisi choti choti baatein hoti rehti hain,\u201d which translates to \"In big countries, such small things happen.\" This line is often used in a humorous context, especially when a player makes a silly mistake.\n\nCricket commentary in Hindi is filled with light-hearted banter and puns, so you'll frequently come across these amusing lines that capture the excitement of the game while also entertaining the audience.",
